    <div class="box">✔ Ideal for TVs and remote-controlled platforms</div>
    <div class="box">✔ Official Plex-recommended method</div>
</div>

<h2>Step-by-Step: How to Activate Plex Using Plex.tv/link</h2>
<ol>
    <li>Install and open the Plex app on your Smart TV or streaming device</li>
    <li>Wait for the 4-digit activation code to appear on the screen</li>
    <li>On a separate device, open a web browser and go to <a href="https://plex.tv/link" target="_blank">plex.tv/link</a></li>
    <li>Log in using your Plex account credentials</li>
    <li>Enter the activation code exactly as shown</li>
    <li>Confirm the action and wait for the success message</li>
</ol>

